getmeson.py
===========

description
-----------
A python script that downloads a release of meson to ./meson and checks its
hash. Use it in your projects if you don't want to require users to `pip
install meson`. Is compatible with python 3.5 and up.

-n: dry run (print what is going to be downloaded)

exit status
-----------
Exit code of zero is good, it means you already have meson or the download was
successful.

